# Network Design & Core Services Configuration

This project demonstrates the design and configuration of a small business network, including subnetting, DHCP, DNS, and email server functionality. The network was planned and implemented using Cisco Packet Tracer.

---

## üéØ Objective
- Design a functional network for 3 subnets
- Configure core network services for host communication
- Verify secure and reliable end-to-end connectivity

---

## üß© Subnet Design
An IPv4 address block was subnetted to support 3 networks, with correct:
- Network addresses
- Host ranges
- Broadcast addresses
- Subnet mask (/27)

Subnet planning table included in the full report.

