## ‚öôÔ∏è Configured Network Services
| Service | Function |
|--------|----------|
| DHCP | Automated IP assignment for clients |
| DNS | Resolving hostnames to IP addresses |
| SMTP / POP3 Email | End-to-end communication between hosts |
| Static Routing | Multi-subnet communication |

---

## üîç Connectivity Verification
- Ping tests between hosts successful
- Email exchanged successfully through configured server
- Router successfully routed traffic between subnets

